      ]
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Usually no treatment required in ED\nACEi\nor\nARB\nfor hypertension, Cr >1.2, or macroalbuminuria\nCorticosteroids\nand/or\ncyclophosphamide\nfor advanced or rapidly progressive disease",
